articles.title: Belarus jails Nobel winner Bialiatski for 10 years; EU, US protest - Reuters
articles.description: Nobel Peace Prize winner and human rights activist Ales Bialiatski was sentenced to 10 years in prison on Friday by a court in his native Belarus which found him guilty of financing protests in a trial condemned by the United States and the European Union as …
